{"heading":"The love of money is the root of all evil—Fight the good fight of faith—Do not trust in worldly riches.","number":6,"verseCount":21,"verses":[[1,["Let as many ",["servants",["study-note-ref","a",["GR slaves. ",["Col. 3:22","nt/col/3.22"],"; ",["Titus 2:9 (9–10)","nt/titus/2.9"],"; ",["1 Pet. 2:18","nt/1-pet/2.18"],"."]]]," as are under the ",["yoke",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Bondage, Physical","tg/bondage-physical"],"."]]]," count their own masters worthy of all honour, that the name of God and ",["his",["clarity-word"]]," doctrine be not blasphemed."]],[2,["And they that have believing masters, let them not despise ",["them,",["clarity-word"]]," because they are ",["brethren",["study-note-ref","a",[["1 Jn. 3:14 (10–18)","nt/1-jn/3.14"],"."]]],"; but rather do ",["them",["clarity-word"]]," ",["service",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Service","tg/service"],"."]]],", because they are faithful and beloved, partakers of the benefit. These things teach and exhort."]],[3,["If any man ",["teach",["study-note-ref","a",[["1 Tim. 1:3","nt/1-tim/1.3"],"; ",["D&C 10:68","dc-testament/dc/10.68"],"."]]]," otherwise, and consent not to ",["wholesome",["study-note-ref","b",[["Titus 2:8","nt/titus/2.8"],"."]]]," words, ",["even",["clarity-word"]]," the words of our Lord Jesus Christ, and to the doctrine which is according to godliness;"]],[4,["He is ",["proud",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Pride","tg/pride"],"."]]],", knowing nothing, but ",["doting",["study-note-ref","b",["GR obsessed with questions."]]]," about ",["questions",["study-note-ref","c",[["1 Tim. 1:4","nt/1-tim/1.4"],"."]]]," and ",["strifes",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Strife","tg/strife"],"."]]]," of words, whereof cometh ",["envy",["study-note-ref","e",[["TG Envy","tg/envy"],"."]]],", strife, railings, ",["evil surmisings",["study-note-ref","f",["GR wicked suspicions."]]],","]],[5,["Perverse ",["disputings",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Disputations","tg/disputations"],"."]]]," of men of corrupt minds, and des